                                      </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </div>
            <div></div>
                      	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px 0px 0px 10px; width:auto; float:left; text-align:left;">
          	  <span class="gn13b">[1955-1 淡水中學白話字史料(修編) 文類-小說 作者--/-]</span>
          	  <a href="artical-src13203.htm"><img src="../images/icon_photo.gif" border="0" align="absmiddle" />&nbsp;<span class="be13b">(24)</span></a>          	  <br />
          	  <span class="be13b"><a href="artical-13203.htm">Lek-sī-ka的代誌 [ Lek-sī-ka ê tāi-chì ]</a></span>
          	  <br />
              <span class="gy12">...<a href="artical-13203.htm"><img src="../images/btn_more.gif" hspace="5" border="0" align="absmiddle" /></a></span>
            </div>
          </td>
